-name beamchain@127.0.0.1
-setcookie beamchain

## Process limit — 1M processes for concurrent peer/block handling
+P 1048576

## Enable kernel polling for better I/O scalability
+K true

## Async thread pool for NIF/driver I/O (RocksDB, secp256k1)
+A 64

## Reduce fullsweep GC frequency for long-lived processes
-env ERL_FULLSWEEP_AFTER 10

## Increase atom table for dynamic peer/config atoms
+t 1048576
